                </mxCell>
                <mxCell id="60" value="&lt;b&gt;Stage 1:&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;1.Create a simple SW_under_test which has the Scheduling functions, in/out interfaces and services (including Scheduling functions)&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;2. Create protobuf file to describe the SW_under_test interfaces and services&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;3. Build the protobuf file and implement the generated grpc services to wrap the SW_under_test interface and services&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;4. Successfully Build the SW_under_test + protobuf&amp;nbsp;stuffer -&amp;gt; this is the vECU&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;5. Create the simple grpc Client to interact with the created vECU" style="rounded=0;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fontSize=12;strokeColor=#000000;strokeWidth=1;align=left;verticalAlign=top;" vertex="1" parent="1">
                    <mxGeometry x="3770" y="965" width="340" height="245" as="geometry"/>
                </mxCell>
                <mxCell id="61" value="&lt;b&gt;Stage 2:&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;1. Replace the simple SW_under_test by the SW needed to be test (HONDA PKlib as a nominated)&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;2. Similar to Stage 1&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;3. Similar to Stage 1&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;4. Similar to Stage 1&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;5. Create the grpc Client to interact with the created vECU,&amp;nbsp;" style="rounded=0;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fontSize=12;strokeColor=#000000;strokeWidth=1;align=left;verticalAlign=top;" vertex="1" parent="1">
                    <mxGeometry x="4220" y="965" width="320" height="245" as="geometry"/>
                </mxCell>
                <mxCell id="62" value="&lt;b&gt;Stage 3:&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;1.Automate the Steps 2-3-4 to build the vECU&amp;nbsp;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;2. Create the Testing-App&lt;br&gt;2.1 The tester can trigger vECU grpc service and show the response&lt;br&gt;2.2 The vECU interface is automatically poplated to the Test-App window from the proto file" style="rounded=0;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fontSize=12;strokeColor=#000000;strokeWidth=1;align=left;verticalAlign=top;" vertex="1" parent="1">
                    <mxGeometry x="4640" y="965" width="320" height="245" as="geometry"/>
                </mxCell>
                <mxCell id="63" value="&lt;b&gt;Stage 4:&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;1. Create a Auto-Test container to test the vECU automatically with the pre-defined Test Action and Test Expectation (defined by the tester)" style="rounded=0;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fontSize=12;strokeColor=#000000;strokeWidth=1;align=left;verticalAlign=top;" vertex="1" parent="1">
                    <mxGeometry x="3770" y="1277.5" width="320" height="245" as="geometry"/>
                </mxCell>
                <mxCell id="64" value="&lt;b&gt;Stage 5:&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;1. Create the Compose to manage all container" style="rounded=0;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fontSize=12;strokeColor=#000000;strokeWidth=1;align=left;verticalAlign=top;" vertex="1" parent="1">
                    <mxGeometry x="4220" y="1277.5" width="320" height="245" as="geometry"/>
                </mxCell>
                <mxCell id="65" value="&lt;b&gt;Stage 6:&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;1. Refine the project structure" style="rounded=0;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fontSize=12;strokeColor=#000000;strokeWidth=1;align=left;verticalAlign=top;" vertex="1" parent="1">
                    <mxGeometry x="4640" y="1277.5" width="320" height="245" as="geometry"/>
                </mxCell>
                <mxCell id="66" value="&lt;b&gt;Stage 7:&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;1. Prepare the Guidance for AI to automate analyze the requirement and create the test&amp;nbsp; then auto run the test on every PR/Push" style="rounded=0;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fontSize=12;strokeColor=#000000;strokeWidth=1;align=left;verticalAlign=top;" vertex="1" parent="1">
                    <mxGeometry x="3770" y="1610" width="320" height="245" as="geometry"/>
                </mxCell>
                <mxCell id="67" value="&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(0 , 0 , 0) ; font-family: &amp;#34;helvetica&amp;#34; ; font-size: 12px ; font-style: normal ; font-weight: 400 ; letter-spacing: normal ; text-indent: 0px ; text-transform: none ; word-spacing: 0px ; background-color: rgb(248 , 249 , 250) ; display: inline ; float: none&quot;&gt;These 2 methods has the same goals:&lt;br&gt;1. Create the enviroment to run the SW under test&lt;br&gt;2. Provide the method to link the SW under test with the&amp;nbsp;enviroment created above&lt;br&gt;3. Has debugging ability&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;" style="text;html=1;strokeColor=none;fillColor=none;align=left;verticalAlign=top;whiteSpace=wrap;rounded=0;" vertex="1" parent="1">
                    <mxGeometry x="3795" y="-40" width="290" height="85" as="geometry"/>
                </mxCell>
                <mxCell id="68" value="" style="endArrow=classic;html=1;rounded=0;endFill=1;exitX=0.127;exitY=1.006;exitDx=0;exitDy=0;exitPerimeter=0;" edge="1" parent="1" source="4" target="67">
